Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.40,0:00:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在場證明！暗號！陷阱！交易！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣組織超神秘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.20,0:00:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的舞臺是古老的城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.00,0:00:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偵探團就要在此展開大冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.70,0:00:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.30,0:00:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 卻擁有過人智慧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名偵探柯南！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.62,0:00:17.33,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,QUEST FOR LOVE  QUEST FOR DREAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.37,0:00:18.71,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,QUEST FOR ALL TRUTH!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.87,0:00:21.79,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,唯有藏在眼神中的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.92,0:00:24.71,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,誰也無法奪走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.00,0:00:31.43,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就優雅地擁抱這個真相吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.60,0:00:43.23,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺肩上的溫暖 和你那不止的淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.44,0:00:49.49,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就在黎明之前 要脫胎換骨 讓自己變得更強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.78,0:00:55.62,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,縱使兩人海角天涯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.87,0:00:59.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,也能夠讓時間停止 找到彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.12,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有愛存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.25,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,QUEST FOR LOVE  QUEST FOR DREAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.75,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,QUEST FOR ALL TRUTH!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.92,0:01:09.76,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,無法制止的熱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.92,0:01:12.76,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,吸引著我倆追求的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.93,0:01:15.89,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這份情感的由來 正是你和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.18,0:01:17.64,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,QUEST FOR LOVE  QUEST FOR DREAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.68,0:01:19.14,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,QUEST FOR ALL TRUTH!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.31,0:01:22.19,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,唯有藏在眼神中的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.48,0:01:25.31,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,誰也無法奪走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.48,0:01:31.74,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就優雅地擁抱這個真相吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊可以眺望得很遠 真不錯啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂～快點來啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.10,0:01:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼冷的天氣 沒事出來露什麼營啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.10,0:02:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當小朋友還真好 總是這麼有活力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有魚耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.80,0:02:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪邊？在哪邊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.20,0:02:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先把帳棚拿出來吧 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.60,0:02:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.30,0:02:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帳棚… 帳棚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.20,0:02:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.70,0:02:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.30,0:02:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會想告訴我 你連帳棚都忘了帶吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我還真的忘了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太誇張了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.90,0:02:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真掃興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.60,0:02:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出來露營居然會忘了最重要的帳棚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.90,0:02:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易的假期 就這樣被搞砸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.70,0:02:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我們好像還迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.00,0:02:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不都是因為你們幾個在旁邊嘮嘮叨叨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.70,0:02:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們今晚得睡車上餵蚊子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不會吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這路上一定會有旅館什麼的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.20,0:02:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是可以看到湖面的城堡之類…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.90,0:02:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 好像不是想太多耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.90,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青色古堡探索事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像西方國家的城堡一樣耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在森林裡頭怎麼會有這種建築物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.20,0:03:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是不知道哪個有錢人家在國外買了這個城堡後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解體送回國內重建的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 元太 你想幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.40,0:03:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是要進去裡面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.90,0:03:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪來的臭小鬼 居然隨便亂闖！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.80,0:03:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的 我們不是什麼壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你們是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是路過此地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,途中見到這座華麗的城堡才停下來看看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.90,0:03:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話 是不是可以讓我們進去參觀一下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們快滾吧！這可不是讓你們這些外人隨便參觀的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.80,0:03:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那些人是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姑爺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.10,0:04:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得今天沒有客人要來吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.50,0:04:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個一臉白癡的老頭子說要進來參觀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰一臉白癡啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是堂堂一名科學家耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科學家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.20,0:04:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我叫做阿笠 算是個小有名氣的發明家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.70,0:04:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 你的頭腦應該比我們這些凡夫俗子更加靈光吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好 請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.20,0:04:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌棄的話 就在舍下住一宿吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦！這真是太感謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 姑爺 沒跟老夫人商量過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就告訴老夫人 他們是我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽已經是那個樣子了 這個理由應該夠敷衍她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.60,0:04:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.40,0:04:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.50,0:04:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也差不多可以放我下來了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這庭院還真大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有馬耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 還有黑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這些馬怎麼只有頭呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那隻馬是西洋棋裡面的騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.00,0:05:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是西洋棋的棋子之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西洋棋的棋子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊不只有棋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看看腳下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很像棋盤格的樣子吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這塊草皮被拿來當作棋盤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.70,0:05:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有人很喜歡西洋棋嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.90,0:05:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我照著前任姑爺 也就是篠昭姑爺的吩咐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.00,0:05:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天稍做整理 藉以維持原狀罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.70,0:05:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說 這是十五年前去世的老爺臨死前交代篠昭姑爺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說前任的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那剛剛那位呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.00,0:05:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 他是小姐入贅的第二任丈夫 阿滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.60,0:05:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,篠昭姑爺在六年前就已經病死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.50,0:05:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而小姐也在四年前因為一場大火而過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.40,0:05:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大火？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.80,0:06:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個被燒毀的塔就是小姐的寢室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.00,0:06:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐為了替老夫人慶生而趕回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到家沒多久就發生火災
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.80,0:06:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐半夜抵家 天還沒亮火就燒起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.90,0:06:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是小姐 還有小姐帶回來的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長年侍奉老夫人的傭人等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.40,0:06:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一共有十幾人被活活燒死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,僥倖存活下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.40,0:06:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了像我這種被雇來作粗活的粗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.50,0:06:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有因為感冒而在別館休息的老夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.90,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及比老夫人還早一步抵達別館的阿滿姑爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.90,0:06:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那邊那位是小姐和篠昭姑爺所生的獨生子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.50,0:06:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴人少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.60,0:06:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是在火災的兩三天前回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.40,0:07:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他很小就被送到國外留學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.20,0:07:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次和他見面 就是在那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.80,0:07:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時那也是我首次和阿滿姑爺見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐是在國外再婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.90,0:07:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直和阿滿姑爺住在海外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.90,0:07:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 不知為何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.80,0:07:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴人少爺在那場火災過後就在這邊住了下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是什麼原因驅使他這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.90,0:07:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當初他們要進入這座城堡 也是困難重重吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認識他們的人根本不多嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.50,0:07:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 小姐曾經把結婚照寄回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家都認識阿滿姑爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於貴人少爺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.90,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟去世的老爺長得像是同一個模子印出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要看過這張畫像 誰都會知道他們是祖孫關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這兩邊的肖像呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是篠昭姑爺和小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.80,0:08:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入贅的篠昭姑爺 對於身為歷史學家的老爺十分敬重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.40,0:08:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也因為如此 姑爺常常被小姐罵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.60,0:08:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我爸他只不過是個滿口大道理的偽知識份子”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.90,0:08:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.50,0:08:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！老夫人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.60,0:08:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些話 你們老爺都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.30,0:08:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他卻沒有因此生氣反而覺得開心哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.80,0:08:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你想起這些傷心的往事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個沒有他在的城堡 我早就習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.50,0:08:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像鈔票和護照大小的改變一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.20,0:08:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始還需要去適應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.00,0:08:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間一久 那種怪怪的感覺也就慢慢變淡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.80,0:08:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光陰真的是可怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.70,0:08:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是悲是喜 都能夠將之磨滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老夫人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這些人是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.60,0:09:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…他是姑爺的朋友 好像是位科學家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科學家…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.60,0:09:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真令人期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.60,0:09:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你務必幫忙解開我先生在這城堡裡留下的謎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.90,0:09:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是老爺臨死前交代的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.40,0:09:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠解開城堡之謎的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就把我最喜歡的寶貝給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.70,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了…我女兒還沒回來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.30,0:09:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了替我慶生 她今天應該會到吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…老夫人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.80,0:09:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她到了以後 叫她立刻到我房裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真開心～真開心～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老夫人自從火災後 一直都是這個樣子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是驚嚇過度吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.00,0:09:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有哪個房間 可以看到庭院裡所有棋子的擺飾啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到院子裡的棋子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有棋子的排列都清晰可見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在哪啊？我沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,元太 你不要擠我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這個房間也可以看得很清楚喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棋子的排列方式 有什麼特殊意義嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.80,0:10:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.40,0:10:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你最喜歡的暗號吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.10,0:10:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…雖然喜歡暗號…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！你們兩個在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會跌下去的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個臭豬頭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.50,0:10:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個在幹嘛啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差點就掉下去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.10,0:10:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,窗戶就緊鄰著牆壁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.60,0:11:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個房間的窗子也是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…這中間的部分到底是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.90,0:11:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種機關 真是老套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.60,0:11:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是把時鐘的指標指向某個地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？柯南？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才不是還在這邊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.90,0:11:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.30,0:11:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是個普通的城堡嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情變得越來越有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？有樓梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？這地方還真深啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個樓梯到底通到哪裡去呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.40,0:11:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？柯南他人不見了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他剛剛不是還在那個房間裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.60,0:12:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.70,0:12:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉眼間他就不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.10,0:12:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椅子被弄倒在地上 散落一地的書…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有蓋子被打開的時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.50,0:12:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個鐘還是壞的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.90,0:12:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.70,0:12:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.00,0:12:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以亂動 要是弄壞了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們幾個怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 只是在惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惡作劇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.40,0:12:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們才沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.40,0:12:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南不見了 我們正在找他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南不見了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.00,0:13:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是跑去上廁所了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廁所就在樓下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們過去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.40,0:13:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要去上廁所 就跟我們說他要去上廁所就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.50,0:13:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？這就怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不在裡面耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的廁所在哪邊呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.10,0:13:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊平時都沒人用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.10,0:13:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有這個廁所…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.50,0:13:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定那小子正躲在哪個地方 準備突然跑出來嚇我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南他最小孩子氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群小鬼不也是孩子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴人少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的份也都準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要現在去吃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是鰻魚飯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果不把柯南找出來的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.30,0:13:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 等他肚子餓了 就會忍不住跑出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們開動了～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾這樣熱鬧一下也很不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 自從媽媽死於那場火災後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到這邊拜訪的客人也日漸稀少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.20,0:14:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說兩位自從火災後就在此長住了 有什麼原因嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.50,0:14:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就打算在國外的大學畢業後就搬回來住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.90,0:14:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一開始是為了陪伴失去獨生女的岳母才留下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.40,0:14:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 日子一久 卻愛上了我太太出生的這個城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.90,0:14:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼！我看你喜歡的不是這座城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.00,0:14:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是城堡裡藏的寶藏吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.60,0:14:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說不在意岳父大人的遺言 那也未免太過矯情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.50,0:14:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到我女兒居然會愛上你這種貪婪的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我的晚餐拿到房裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.80,0:15:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐回來了就把她帶來見我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.80,0:15:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非得好好臭駡她一頓不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.70,0:15:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外婆還是老樣子 一直以為媽媽還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會這樣混亂也不是沒道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.90,0:15:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從她因為腳痛需要靠著輪椅行動後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.50,0:15:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經待在這個城堡裡頭 十年足不出戶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 謎底你已經解開了吧？阿笠先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.80,0:15:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？你還沒聽說嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據我岳父的遺言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要解開城堡裡的謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.90,0:15:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以得到我最愛的寶貝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.00,0:15:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這個 我已經從田畑園丁那邊聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.10,0:15:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我也不知從何著手才好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.80,0:15:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是擺在庭院裡的那些西洋棋呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.80,0:15:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.30,0:15:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在庭院裡面那個西洋棋棋盤是藏寶人有意打造的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.90,0:15:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那些棋子本身應該藏有寶藏的相關線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點應該錯不了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的假的啊？小哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.20,0:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你知道那些棋子所代表的意義？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.30,0:16:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能知道呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.10,0:16:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們花了四年都還沒解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說有人可以解開的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.70,0:16:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是那個在城堡裡不知所蹤 好奇心旺盛的推理狂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推…推理狂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 塑膠袋 這種的可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.70,0:16:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿塑膠袋幹嘛啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想把我的麵包留一個給柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他大概也肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.10,0:16:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那個戴眼鏡的小朋友怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…從剛才我們就一直找不到他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.40,0:16:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃飽後再繼續找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城堡的結構太過錯綜複雜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.30,0:16:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好他迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他不是在那個塔裡走失才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.70,0:16:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個塔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.90,0:16:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從城堡的左手邊望去就看得到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.80,0:17:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是四年前我妻子被燒死在裡面的塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在被森林所包圍 上面有著焦黑痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.30,0:17:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在兩年前 我們家中新請的傭人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在帶他熟悉城堡的時候 突然下落不明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一問之下 才知道 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.80,0:17:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他常常對其他傭人說 那座塔裡面十分的棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此我們立刻趕到那座塔裡去找人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.60,0:17:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那裡面不但沒有任何人侵入的痕跡 他人更是不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.80,0:17:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來我們報警在這一帶的森林裡展開大規模搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十天後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.60,0:17:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於在森林裡面找到了已經被活活餓死的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.20,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方是把這個案子當作是誤闖森林而餓死的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這件事情卻成了流言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.50,0:17:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在傭人之間口耳相傳了好一陣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.20,0:18:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們認為這是被燒死在塔中的怨靈作祟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會使得他死於非命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.70,0:18:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此後那座塔的出入口就被封了起來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.50,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那如果我們不快點找到柯南的話 他搞不好會餓死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 把我的麵包也留一個給他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.50,0:18:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.60,0:18:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們趁著天還沒黑 快點分頭去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂～柯南～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再躲了 快點出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來他不在院子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城堡裡面我們也全都找過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.00,0:18:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是一無所獲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.10,0:18:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 最有可能的還是在那座塔裡了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.50,0:18:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我剛才到入口那邊看過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門還是鎖著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 只有森林裡還沒找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.80,0:18:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 雨越下越大了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.70,0:18:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上進入森林裡 也十分危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要展開搜查的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是明天一早請求警方協助才是上策吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個先回屋裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.90,0:19:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.30,0:19:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.70,0:19:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.90,0:19:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川他不是那種會讓你擔心的弱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.50,0:19:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是那種可以靠著自己逃出生天的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其在那邊哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.10,0:19:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如把袋子封好 免得麵包被雨淋濕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.00,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.80,0:19:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣淋雨會感冒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 快回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼這麼了解柯南呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…到底為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.10,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道…難道你喜歡柯南？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.40,0:19:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的話 那又怎樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.80,0:19:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我會很為難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.40,0:20:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.70,0:20:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在我心裡根本無足輕重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不騙人喔～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的小孩子也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你說的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一他不會有問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.10,0:20:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有求助就是最好的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.60,0:20:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼傻話啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.80,0:20:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為他會平白無故會消失幾個鐘頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.50,0:20:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點音訊也沒有 讓我們在這裡乾著急嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是出事了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.30,0:20:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是被這個城堡裡的人給軟禁了 無法逃脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被殺了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.00,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前當務之急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.10,0:20:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是趁著城堡裡的人不注意 先與警方取得連絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.40,0:20:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便展開搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.80,0:20:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 要找地方的不是森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.80,0:20:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是城堡內部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有頭緒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.00,0:21:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤不在的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.80,0:21:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能夠依靠的 就只有身為大人的你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.30,0:21:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.10,0:21:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…電話…電話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.10,0:21:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.10,0:21:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了 有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是新一的帽子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.30,0:21:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這道門是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.20,0:21:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.40,0:21:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然要報警 不如找我們認識橫溝警官或是目暮警官…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.20,0:22:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.80,0:22:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.00,0:23:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那元太他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.10,0:23:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是落在那個跟蹤我們的人手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.20,0:23:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.00,0:23:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不對…那不是灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.30,0:24:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是柯南的眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.70,0:24:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的目標恐怕是這個城堡裡的財寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.00,0:24:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下周的柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.50,0:24:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青色古城搜索事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.60,0:24:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.30,0:24:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,護照的尺寸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.00,0:24:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一集揭曉的兇手 是個意想不到的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.80,0:24:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他！一定是他沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.96,0:22:27.59,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個看似有事即將發生的夜裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.13,0:22:32.26,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,不要閉上雙眼 誠心祝禱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.05,0:22:38.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽曾經說過 月光如此澄澈的夜裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.22,0:22:44.98,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是因愛而出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.53,0:22:56.24,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,接著一切都停滯不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.87,0:23:02.54,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的未來已經碎為片片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.83,0:23:11.26,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,來 打著赤腳 輕踢大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.42,0:23:16.72,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,越過彩虹 抓住天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.51,0:23:23.23,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Wish 緊緊握住胸口的十字架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.35,0:23:29.48,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在白天 用希望照耀著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.65,0:23:35.70,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在夜晚 以溫柔的光芒將你輕輕包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.86,0:23:42.49,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever still for you, still for you love
